@startuml
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
skinparam roundcorner 12

actor User
participant "Frontend / Browser" as Browser
participant "OAuthLogin Handler" as LoginHandler
participant "Authentication UseCase" as AuthUC
participant "OAuth Provider" as Provider
participant "OAuthCallback Handler" as CallbackHandler
participant "User Repository" as UserRepo
participant "JWT Manager" as JWTMgr
participant "Session Manager" as SessionMgr

User -> Browser: Chọn đăng nhập
Browser -> LoginHandler: GET /authentication/login?redirect=...
LoginHandler -> LoginHandler: processLoginRequest()
LoginHandler -> AuthUC: InitiateOAuthLogin(state)
AuthUC -> Provider: GetAuthCodeURL(state)
Provider --> AuthUC: authURL
AuthUC --> LoginHandler: authURL
LoginHandler --> Browser: 307 Redirect đến OAuth provider

User -> Provider: Đăng nhập và chấp thuận
Provider --> Browser: Redirect callback với code + state
Browser -> CallbackHandler: GET /authentication/callback
CallbackHandler -> CallbackHandler: processCallbackRequest()
CallbackHandler -> AuthUC: ProcessOAuthCallback(code)
AuthUC -> Provider: ExchangeCode(code)
Provider --> AuthUC: access token
AuthUC -> Provider: GetUserInfo(token)
Provider --> AuthUC: user info
AuthUC -> UserRepo: createOrUpdateUser(...)
UserRepo --> AuthUC: user
AuthUC -> JWTMgr: generateToken(user, role)
JWTMgr --> AuthUC: jwt + jti
AuthUC -> SessionMgr: createSession(userId, jti)
SessionMgr --> AuthUC: ok
AuthUC --> CallbackHandler: token
CallbackHandler --> Browser: Set auth cookie + redirect
@enduml
